# DebugPanelSystem  (sbx)

## Purpose
Renders the ImGui debug panel and owns DebugControlsSingletonComponent. Lazily creates the controls
singleton on the first frame. On later frames it draws an ImGui window exposing an animation-speed
slider (written back into DebugControlsSingletonComponent, which QuadAnimationSystem reads) plus
read-only readouts of the spawn count and live input state. All ImGui calls are skipped when no
ImGui context exists (e.g. under the test build, which has no ImGuiLayer), so there the system only
maintains the controls singleton.

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| SpawnerSingletonComponent | read | Spawn-count readout (optional) |
| InputStateSingletonComponent | read | Mouse position / held-key readout (optional) |
| DebugControlsSingletonComponent | write | Animation-speed slider value |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| DebugControlsSingletonComponent | write / add (deferred) | Created once; m_AnimationSpeed driven by the ImGui slider |
